<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jared Adams | Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #f8fafc;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #38bdf8;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .links {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 350px;
        }
        .link-card {
            background-color: #1e293b;
            color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        }
        .link-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            border-color: #38bdf8;
        }
        .link-card strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        .link-card span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Jared Adams</h1>
    <h2>US Air Force Veteran | Computer Science Student <br> </h2>

    <div class="links">
        <a href="agency.html" class="link-card">
            <strong>OkayJerd AI Agency</strong>
            <span>My automated missed call text system</span>
        </a>
        // <a href="https://github.com/okayjerd" class="link-card">
